# D{{N}} — Domain-Capability Map

**Audience:** Stakeholder (plain-language labels). Partners, investors, new hires.
**When to look at this:** First thing when joining the project. Before reading any prose.
**Prose gap closed:** No existing capability decomposition — readers had to infer business shape from individual BC canvases.

